quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  30,51,"[Hay] si Men nulii henndu, …ìe yi'i [gese ma…ì…ìe] …óen no soy…ói, …ìe jokkay …ìaawo …óum, hi…ìe yedda"
  30,52,"Pellet, an a nanintaa maay…ìe …ìen, a nanintaa faa…óu…ìe …ìen kadi noddaandu ndun, si …ìe runtiima …ìe huccinii …ìabbe (ma…ì…ìe)"
  30,53,"A wonaali fewnoowo wum…ìe …ìen e majjere ma…ì…ìe. A nanintaa si wanaa …ìen gom…óim…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen, hara ko …ìe jebbilii…ìe"
  30,54,"Ko Alla woni tagu…óo on e lo'ere, refti O wa…ói …ìaawo lo'ere nden cemmbe, refti O wa…ói …ìaawo cemmbe …óen lo'ere e puri(dandanndi). Himo taga ko O muuyi, Ko Kanko woni Anndu…óo, Hattan…óo"
  30,55,"√ëalnde Darngal nal darotoo, bom…ìe …ìen woonday …ìe √±ii…ìaali si wanaa saanga. Ko wano nii …ìe wonanoo ferliseede (e goonga)"
  30,56,"Okkaa…ìe ganndal e gom…óinal …ìen wi'a: \"Gom…óii on √±ii…ìii e ko Alla winndi kon, haa √±alnde ummital. Ko ndee woni √±alaande ummital, kono onon on anndaano"
  30,57,"Nden √±alnde, ngantooji …óin nafoytaa too√±u…ìe …ìen, wanaa kam…ìe woni ko …óa…ì…ìiretee welayee [Alla]. @Corrected"
  30,58,"Gom…óii Men piyanii yim…ìe …ìen e nde Alquraanaa- re, kala misal. Pellet, si a addanii …ìe Aaya, …ìen yeddu…ìe wi'ay: \"On wonaali, si wanaa meerentee…ìe"
  30,59,Ko wano nii Alla notira e …ìer…óe …ìen …ìe anndaa
  30,60,"Mu√±√±o, pellet, fodoore Alla nden, ko goona. Wata …ìe hoynuma …ìen hoyfine"
